{"parents": [{"link": "../../../", "title": "The Platform"}, {"link": "../../", "title": "Guides"}], "prev": {"link": "../filter_or/", "title": "The <strong>OR</strong> Conditional"}, "next": {"link": "../how_to_edit/", "title": "Editing"}, "title": "Grid Setup", "meta": null, "body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"grid-setup\">\n<h1>Grid Setup<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#grid-setup\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<div class=\"admonition note\">\n<p class=\"admonition-title\">Note</p>\n<p>The Grid is the name for the interface used on the Maha Platform.</p>\n<p>Across all the sections of the Maha Platform, from the <strong>CRM</strong> to <strong>Finance</strong>, the Grid along with a couple of useful features allows efficient, sensible navigation.</p>\n<p>While not every feature is available for each section, below is a comprehensive list of the features with which you might want to be familiar.</p>\n<p>Click on the hyperlink to get to a detailed instructional guide on how to use each feature!</p>\n</div>\n<ol class=\"arabic simple\">\n<li><p><a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/general/guides/how_to_search.html\">Search</a> through records to pull up a specific result</p></li>\n<li><p><a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/general/guides/how_to_upload_a_file.html\">Reload</a> records to refresh the page</p></li>\n<li><p><a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/general/guides/exporting_records.html\">Export</a> records to download or send data</p></li>\n<li><p><a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/general/guides/how_to_filter_records.html\">Filter</a> records to narrow search results according to criteria</p></li>\n<li><p><a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/general/guides/how_to_edit.html\">Edit</a> a record</p></li>\n<li><p><a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/general/guides/how_to_comment.html\">Comment</a> on a record</p></li>\n<li><p><a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/general/guides/display_elements.html\">Add or hide columns</a> of a row (eg. ID, codes)</p></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n", "metatags": "", "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["users/general/guides/functions_of_the_grid/how_to_edit", "Editing", "N", "next"], ["users/general/guides/functions_of_the_grid/filter_or", "The <strong>OR</strong> Conditional", "P", "previous"]], "sourcename": "users/general/guides/functions_of_the_grid/grid_setup.rst.txt", "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">Grid Setup</a></li>\n</ul>\n", "display_toc": false, "page_source_suffix": ".rst", "current_page_name": "users/general/guides/functions_of_the_grid/grid_setup", "sidebars": ["localtoc.html", "relations.html", "sourcelink.html", "searchbox.html"], "customsidebar": null, "favicon_url": null, "logo_url": null, "alabaster_version": "0.7.12"}